==English==

===Etymology===
From Latin ''[[thesaurus]]'', treasure.

===Noun===
'''treasure''' (''[[countable]] and [[uncountable]]'', ''plural'' [[treasures]])
# {{uncountable}}: A collection of valuable things.
#:''buried '''treasure'''.''
# {{countable}}: Any single thing one values greatly.
# {{countable}}: A [[term of endearment]].

